    "body": "Fix:\r\n```diff\r\ndiff --git a/mods/ra/maps/monster-tank-madness/monster-tank-madness.lua b/mods/ra/maps/monster-tank-madness/monster-tank-madness.lua\r\nindex 24cbec8..5813bca 100644\r\n--- a/mods/ra/maps/monster-tank-madness/monster-tank-madness.lua\r\n+++ b/mods/ra/maps/monster-tank-madness/monster-tank-madness.lua\r\n@@ -131,6 +131,7 @@ SuperTankDomeInfiltrated = function()\r\n        SuperTankAttack = true\r\n        Utils.Do(SuperTanks, function(tnk)\r\n                tnk.Owner = friendlyMadTanks\r\n+               tnk.GrantCondition(\"friendly\")\r\n                if not tnk.IsDead then\r\n                        Trigger.ClearAll(tnk)\r\n                        tnk.Stop()\r\ndiff --git a/mods/ra/maps/monster-tank-madness/rules.yaml b/mods/ra/maps/monster-tank-madness/rules.yaml\r\nindex 6345be5..be3d57e 100644\r\n--- a/mods/ra/maps/monster-tank-madness/rules.yaml\r\n+++ b/mods/ra/maps/monster-tank-madness/rules.yaml\r\n@@ -64,6 +64,13 @@ PBOX:\r\n                Crushes: wall, mine, crate, infantry\r\n        RevealsShroud:\r\n                Range: 6c0\r\n+               RequiresCondition: !friendly\r\n+       RevealsShroud@friendly:\r\n+               Range: 6c0\r\n+               RequiresCondition: friendly\r\n+               ValidStances: Ally, Enemy\r\n+       ExternalCondition@revealsshroud:\r\n+               Condition: friendly\r\n        Turreted:\r\n                TurnSpeed: 1\r\n        Armament@PRIMARY:\r\n\r\n```"
